# Running Tests – Allure Report

When the user asks to run tests, after the test run also open the Allure report by default (`npm run allure:serve` or `npx allure serve allure-results`).

Skip opening the report only when the user explicitly says they don't want it (e.g. "run tests without report", "just run tests, no report").
